Package: duckbotos-openclaw
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: duckbotos-base,
         duckbotos-brain,
         nodejs (>= 18),
         npm,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenClaw as primary desktop environment for DuckBotOS
 Installs OpenClaw as the primary AI agent and desktop surface
 for DuckBotOS.
 .
 OpenClaw provides:
 - Gateway API at http://localhost:18789
 - openclaw-os web workspace plugin at /plugins/openclawos
 - 40+ built-in tools (shell, file, browser, memory, sub-agents, cron)
 - Multi-channel messaging (Telegram, Signal, etc.)
 - Sub-conscious daemon for long-term memory and pattern recognition
 - Hybrid orchestrator for task routing
 .
 In DuckBotOS, OpenClaw runs as a systemd user service and the
 Weston kiosk loads the openclaw-os workspace in fullscreen Chromium.
 .
 Homepage: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw